high_descs: Turn right and head to the sink on your right.
Pick up the egg from the sink drainer.
Move a few steps to the sink on your right.
Wash the egg in the sink.
Turn right and head across the room to the white table on your right.
Set the egg down on the table in front of the blade of the knife and to the left of the end of the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Put the a clean egg on the table.

high_descs: Turn right, walk to the stove, then turn right again to face the kitchen sink.
Pick up the egg that is sitting on the left sink basin.
Move slightly right over to the right sink basin.
Rinse the egg in the right sink basin before taking it back out.
Turn right, hanging a right when you reach the fridge on your left, and walk up to the table .
Place the egg on the table to the left of the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Move a clean egg to a kitchen table.

high_descs: Turn right, walk forward to the stove top, then turn right and walk to the egg.
Pick up the egg from the counter top.
Walk slightly to the right and face the sink.
Put the egg in the sink, rinse it off, and take it back out.
Turn right, walk to the refrigerator, then turn right and walk to the dining table.
Put the egg on the dining table, to the left of the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned egg on a dining table.
